      <!-- WHY USE -->
      <h2>Why Use a Relationship App?</h2>
      <p>Modern relationships face unique challenges, from busy schedules to digital distractions. Couples therapy and relationship apps bridge the gap between self-help books and traditional counseling. They provide structured, evidence-based exercises, daily prompts, and guided conversations right on your phone — making relationship maintenance accessible, affordable, and engaging.</p>

