        </div>

        <div class="faq-card">
          <h3>What is the difference between a relationship app and couples therapy?</h3>
          <p>Relationship apps typically provide self-guided educational content, quizzes, and structured exercises based on psychological principles to help couples improve communication and connection independently. Traditional couples therapy involves working directly with a licensed professional who provides personalized guidance, mediation, and clinical treatment for complex relationship dynamics. Apps like ReGain and Ours blur this line by offering licensed therapy through an app interface.</p>
